<sect2>
<title>Installation de <application>scrollkeeper</application></title>

<para>Installez <application>scrollkeeper</application> en lançant les commandes
suivantes:</para>

<screen><userinput><command>./configure --prefix=/usr --sysconfdir=/etc \
--localstatedir=/var --disable-static \
--with-omfdirs=/usr/share/omf:/opt/gnome/share/omf:\
/opt/kde/share/omf:/opt/gnome-&gnome-version;/share/omf &amp;&amp;
make &amp;&amp;
make install</command></userinput></screen>

</sect2>

